title: (Thurs Part 2) Morning Corny After Dark + Amy Tries to Match the University with the Mascot + Bobby on a Random Guy Who Was In His House on Wedding Day
itunes:title: (Thurs Part 2) Morning Corny After Dark + Amy Tries to Match the University with the Mascot + Bobby on a Random Guy Who Was In His House on Wedding Day
description:
Per listener request, Amy brings back The Morning Corny after dark. In honor of March Madness, Amy tries to guess the mascot when Bobby gives her the name of the University. Bobby shares a story about how a ‘random guy’ was walking around his house on his wedding day.
